&lt;li&gt;Work with vendors to keep the office stocked with food, snacks, and pantry supplies that meet Datadog standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track office supplies and restock as needed to support daily operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and coordinate engaging employee events—monthly and as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with teammates to keep operations running smoothly and consistently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Operations teams on office moves, build-outs, and openings when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in a 9-month rotation with teammates to gain hands-on experience as project coordinators across key areas including event planning, food program management, space planning, and facilities operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
