&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 2–4 years of administrative or office experience and strong written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re approachable and empathetic, with a polished, professional tone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You build strong relationships and thrive in collaborative environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re organized and detail-driven, with excellent time management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership and move work forward without being asked.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re calm under pressure and help bring clarity to busy days.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re creative, comfortable with spreadsheets, and excited to contribute to team culture.&lt;/li&gt;
